法一: Start 'gparted' and make the partitions

法二：from the terminal
  sudo fdisk -l     #list all disks
  sudo fdisk /dev/xxx        #figure out witch disk is your card
  sudo mkfs -t ext4 /dev/xxx2                     #create filesystems
  
  
some fdisk commands:

  d delete partition
  n create a partition
  l list types
  t set type (c for fat32. 83 for linux)
  w save
  q quit without making any changes  
